    "body": "This is because you have set `--http-port=4001` in your beacon node. \r\n\r\nBy default, the `vc` connects to the `bn` via `http://localhost:5052` (port 5052). So in your case, you need to specify in the vc, `--beacon-nodes http://localhost:4001` to connect to the `bn`",
